        "created_at": "2023-06-25T11:56:50.665Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I’d like to be able to schedule voice messages as well<br>\nSince you don’t get to see the send button in the normal flow I figured it might be possible by backing out of the chat during recording.<br>\nThis leads to the recording being stopped and you seeing a preview plus send button</p>\n<p>However, long pressing the send button doesn’t allow for scheduling in this case<br>\nInstead it informs you that sms messages are disabled<br>\nThis seems unintended to me since the sms functionality has been removed a while ago</p>\n<p>Would make more sense to allow for scheduling, even if leaving and reentering the chat is more of a workaround</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 4,
