        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Aku-Stable\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"54123\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/aku-stable/48/25198_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Aku-Stable:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hopefully this feature will be in Signal v7.39 on Android</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I noticed this feature is already available in v7.38.7 stable on Android <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/slightly_smiling_face.png?v=12\" title=\":slightly_smiling_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slightly_smiling_face:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/+1.png?v=12\" title=\":+1:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":+1:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>From this:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote group-automated_users\" data-username=\"updates-bot\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"67625\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/updates-bot/48/31268_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"><a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/beta-feedback-for-the-upcoming-android-7-38-release/67625/2\">Beta feedback for the upcoming Android 7.38 release</a></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Support scheduled voice notes. <a href=\"//github.com/signalapp/Signal-Android/commit/52c8dfc99880ad31a94e23b3377b6e72c77fb8ad\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">[7]</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Edit: The stable update was available to me on Tuesday 1 April 2025 in the evening, nice silent feature drop for April Fool’s Day <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/smile.png?v=12\" title=\":smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
